        <h3>Houzz Pro — Basic time tracking for smaller crews</h3>
        <p>Houzz Pro includes time tracking functionality at its accessible price point. For smaller contractors with straightforward needs — logging hours, linking to projects, and generating basic reports — it handles the basics well.</p>

